snippet: Missouri’s victory over Texas A&M sealed the Southeastern Conference East, and the Tigers advanced to the conference championship game against Auburn.
abstract: College Football Top 25 Roundup; Missouri wraps up the Southeastern Conference East, riding a strong second half to a 28-21 victory over Texas A&M; other scores noted.
lead_paragraph: Missouri’s victory over Texas A&M sealed the Southeastern Conference East, and the Tigers advanced to the conference championship game against Auburn.

headline.main: Missouri Earns Berth in SEC Title Game
headline.print_headline: Missouri Earns Berth in SEC Title Game
